---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Custom Agents & Autonomous Workflows — rebel-state',
  description: 'Design and deploy agentic workflows that autonomously execute multi-step tasks while providing human oversight.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <Hero
    tagline="Services"
    title="Custom Agents & Autonomous Workflows"
    subtitle="Autonomous agents that research, synthesize, and act — with human-in-the-loop control when needed."
    actions={[{ text: 'Contact us', href: '/contact', variant: 'primary' }]}
  />
  <main class="prose mx-auto max-w-4xl py-12">
    <p>The paradigm of software is shifting from "Tools we use" to "Agents that work for us." At rebel-state, we are at the forefront of the Agentic Revolution. Custom Agents are specialized AI entities capable of executing multi-step tasks with a degree of autonomy that standard automation cannot reach. While traditional automation follows a linear path, an Agent can reason, plan, and adjust its course based on the feedback it receives from its environment.</p>

    <p>We design and deploy these agents to act as a "Digital Workforce." Imagine an agent that doesn't just notify you of a new lead but researches the lead's company, analyzes their recent public filings, drafts a personalized outreach email based on your brand voice, and schedules a follow-up—all without human intervention. This is the level of autonomy rebel-state brings to your workflows. We utilize state-of-the-art frameworks to build agents that can interact with your existing software suite, browse the web for real-time information, and perform complex data synthesis.</p>

    <p>Building autonomous workflows requires a deep understanding of task decomposition. We break down your most complex business goals into high-fidelity sub-tasks that agents can manage reliably. We implement "Human-in-the-loop" (HITL) protocols where necessary, ensuring that while the agent does the heavy lifting, your team maintains ultimate oversight and quality control. This approach minimizes cognitive fatigue and allows for a "Managerial Scale"—where one person can oversee a fleet of agents performing the work of an entire department. Whether it’s autonomous customer support, automated technical documentation, or real-time supply chain optimization, our agents are built to be reliable, secure, and incredibly efficient.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
